    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Projet是FinTech_FraudDetection。那这个项目需要关联哪些参与者？我注意到业务中有推荐人机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Projet",
        "Parrain"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Parrain代表FinTech_AuthVault，是认证中心。一个项目可以有多个Parrain，但每个Parrain最多属于一个项目。另外Parrain需要关联Adresse，也就是FinTech_TransactionQueue。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Parrain",
        "Projet",
        "Adresse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了Parrain到Projet的多对一关系，以及Parrain到Adresse的一对一关联。接下来平台层怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Parrain",
        "Projet",
        "Adresse",
        "Plateforme"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Plateforme是FinTech_LedgerService，账本服务。每个平台由一个Parrain管理，但Parrain可以管理多个平台。平台本身也需要关联Adresse。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Parrain",
        "Adresse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Plateforme到Parrain是多对一，Plateforme到Adresse是一对一。然后支付网关层呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Parrain",
        "Adresse",
        "Porteur"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Porteur是FinTech_PaymentGateway。每个Porteur属于一个平台，但平台可以有多个Porteur。Porteur也需要Adresse，并且一个项目可以有一个Porteur。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Porteur",
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse",
        "Projet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Porteur相关关系。最后用户层Utilisateur如何设计？也是FinTech_FraudDetection？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Utilisateur",
        "Porteur",
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Utilisateur也是FinTech_FraudDetection，代表终端用户实体。每个用户有唯一地址，属于一个平台，平台可以有多个用户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Utilisateur",
